WTF is this crap you can give a pet a weapon ?<P><BR>Q: Is the loot a monster drops determined when it is spawned, or when it dies? <P>A: When it dies. Upon death, the game looks at the loot table and chooses from a list (a list with only one item, for some creatures). This is why, when you give a pet a weapon, you don&#8217;t get the weapon back when the pet dies. The pet has a loot table with nothing on it, regardless of what it might be holding. <P><BR>What ? I am totally confused. How the hell or WHO the hell can give a pet a weapon ?<P>--------------------<P>No, that snapping sound is not your back.  It is your feeble soul...<BR>***********************************<BR>Taiju WillCrusher  37 Sorc / Lancelot - 30 Mind 24 Body<BR>Gulwyn MacFarlane  43 Cleric / Lancelot - 34 Rej 22 Enh 15 Smite
