Well, the weapon has to be 'better' by whatever calculations the MOB/Guard uses to determine that. Armor is much easier to equip them with. If your ever around a keep that has been held for a while, check out some of the guards.... soemtimes it will say that guard has been upgraded. This is why.<P>It does indeed work. Seems that a lot of it is not based so much on the weapon or armors stats, but it's material rank level. L8 material will not overwite a L9 weapon, even if the actual stats on the weapon are better, an would yeild more DPS.<P>--------------------<P>i3ullseye<BR>"You're good, but me? I'm Magic!"<P>Rictus -Sorceror(DAOC)/Rictus(EQ)<BR>DAOC Sorceror team lead...<P>Please visit our <A HREF="http://www.yesterdayland.com/popopedia/shows/toys/ty1050.php" TARGET=_blank>Sponsors!</A>  <IMG SRC="biggrin.gif" border="0">
